# Dispatch HQ — Cursor Rules
# This file is read automatically by Cursor on every interaction.
# Do NOT delete or modify this file's format.

## PROJECT IDENTITY
You are editing Dispatch HQ — a bilingual (English/Korean) taxi dispatch booking web app for NYC.
Single-page application. React 18. Pre-compiled with esbuild. Google Sheets encrypted backend.

## FILE ROLES — CRITICAL

### EDIT THESE:
- `taxi-dispatcher.jsx`     — THE source file. All feature changes go here.
- `google-apps-script.js`   — Backend. Paste into Google Apps Script editor after changes.

### NEVER EDIT DIRECTLY:
- `dispatch-hq.html`        — GENERATED from taxi-dispatcher.jsx via esbuild. Regenerate, never hand-edit.

### Supporting docs (update when features change):
- `codex-handoff.md`, `chatgpt-handoff.md`, `website-deploy-guide.md`

