## STORAGE KEYS — COMPLETE MAP

```javascript
// localStorage
"dispatch-hq-accounts"     → UserAccount[]          (local auth)
"dispatch-hq-sync-config"  → SyncConfig             (GAS endpoint, passphrase hash, lastSync, authToken)
"dispatch-hq-maps-key"     → string                 (Google Maps API key)
"dispatch-hq-gdpr-notice"  → "dismissed"            (GDPR banner state)
"taxi-bookings-data"        → Booking[]              (all bookings, 2yr retention)
"dispatch-hq-backup-{ts}"  → Booking[]              (snapshots, rolling 5)
"dispatch-hq-backup-log"   → BackupLogEntry[]       (100 entries)

// sessionStorage
"dispatch-hq-session"      → SessionObject          (current auth session)
```

