## CORE DATA SHAPES

### Booking (complete, 18 fields)
```typescript
{
  id: string              // 24-char hex, crypto.getRandomValues
  customerName: string
  phone: string           // sanitizePhone() → [0-9+\-().space] only
  pickupAddress: string
  dropoffAddress: string
  airline: string         // "" when !isAirportTrip
  flightNumber: string    // "" when !isAirportTrip; always UPPERCASE
  passengers: string      // "1" default
  luggage: string         // "0" default
  tripType: "one-way" | "round-trip"
  paymentAmount: string   // sanitizeNumeric()
  driverNumber: string    // 2-char padded: "08", "19"
  date: string            // "YYYY-MM-DD"
  timeSlot: string        // "3:00 PM" (12h with space before AM/PM)
  createdAt: string       // ISO 8601
  modifiedAt: string      // ISO 8601 — newer wins on sync conflict
  flightStatus: string    // "On Time" | "Delayed" | ""
  flightArrival: string   // ISO or time string
  fareRoute: string       // "JFK → Manhattan"
  fareBreakdown: string   // "$70 +$8 toll"
}
```

