## ISAIRPORTTRIP — CRITICAL DERIVED STATE (L2467)

```javascript
const isAirportTrip = useMemo(() => {
  const CODES = ["JFK", "LGA", "EWR"];
  return CODES.includes(normalizeLocation(form.pickupAddress)) ||
         CODES.includes(normalizeLocation(form.dropoffAddress));
}, [form.pickupAddress, form.dropoffAddress]);
```

**Drives:**
- Airline/Flight # `required` flag in validation (L~2510)
- Airline/Flight # `disabled` + `opacity:0.25` in UI (L~2610)
- Auto-clear airline/flightNumber on address change (in onChange handlers)
- Fleet Assignment grey-out: `noAirportPU`, `noAirportDO` conditions

**DO NOT** call `normalizeLocation()` inline in render — use this useMemo.

