## FLEET ASSIGNMENT GREYING LOGIC

All four conditions evaluated per driver per render:
```javascript
const offDate     = !shift.available                    // date check via getDriverShift
const offTime     = !offDate && form.timeSlot           // time check via driverTimeMatch useMemo
                     ? !driverTimeMatch[driver.id].available : false
const noAirportPU = needsPickup  && !driver.airportPickup
const noAirportDO = needsDropoff && !driver.airportDropoff

const isUnavailable = offDate || offTime || noAirportPU || noAirportDO

// Reason label priority:
offDate → "Off today"
noAirportPU && noAirportDO → "No airport"
noAirportPU → `No PU at ${pickup}`
noAirportDO → `No DO at ${dropoff}`
offTime → "Off shift"
shift.start → `${fmt12(shift.start)}–${fmt12(shift.end)}`
default → "On duty"
```

Shift time display — always 12h (never military time):
```javascript
const fmt12 = (t) => {
  let [h, m] = t.split(":").map(Number);
  const p = h >= 12 ? "PM" : "AM";
  if (h === 0) h = 12; else if (h > 12) h -= 12;
  return `${h}${m ? ":"+String(m).padStart(2,"0") : ""}${p}`;
};
```

