## GETDRIVERSHIFT — TIMEZONE BUG (FIXED, DO NOT REVERT)

```javascript
// CORRECT — use T12:00:00 to avoid UTC midnight timezone offset
const d = new Date(dateStr + "T12:00:00");
const weekday = d.toLocaleDateString("en-US", { weekday: "long" });

// WRONG — never use this form:
const d = new Date(dateStr);  // UTC midnight → wrong local weekday in some timezones
```

