## WHISPER VOICE INPUT (AddressField)

```javascript
// Model: "Xenova/whisper-tiny" via @xenova/transformers@2.17.2
// CDN: https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@xenova/transformers@2.17.2
// Storage: IndexedDB (permanent cache after first ~40MB download)

// Config:
{
  language: null,          // AUTO-DETECT — never force "korean" or "english"
  task: "transcribe",
  initial_prompt: "주소를 말하고 있습니다. The speaker is saying a street address..."
}

// Toggle: one tap = start recording (MediaRecorder), one tap = stop + transcribe
// States: "idle" → "recording" → "processing" → "done"|"error"
// HIPAA: runs 100% in-browser, no network calls during inference

// Pipeline:
// MediaRecorder → Blob → ArrayBuffer → AudioContext.decodeAudioData
// → resample to 16kHz → Float32Array → asr() → normalizeSpokenNumbers()

// MediaRecorder MIME priority:
["audio/webm;codecs=opus", "audio/webm", "audio/ogg;codecs=opus", "audio/ogg", "audio/mp4", ""]
// Use first supported via MediaRecorder.isTypeSupported()
```

