## PARSÉTRANSCRIPTLOCAL — FIELD EXTRACTION ORDER (DO NOT REORDER)

Fields must be extracted in this order to prevent regex bleed:
```
1. Date    (month names, M/D/YYYY, YYYY-MM-DD, tomorrow, today, 오늘, 내일)
2. Time    (3 PM, 3:30 PM, 오후 3시 → form.timeSlot = "3:00 PM")
3. Payment ($70, 70 dollars, 70달러)
4. Flight  (KE81, flight KE 81, IATA pattern [A-Z]{2}\d{2,5})
5. Airline (known carrier list)
6. Driver  (driver 19, 기사 08)
7. Name    (keyword prefix OR first capitalized words before any keyword)
8. Phone   (10-11 digit pattern)
9. TripType (round-trip|one-way|왕복|편도)
10. Passengers, Luggage
11. CLEANED TEXT → Pickup, Dropoff (after removing matched tokens from string)
12. Airport normalization on pickup/dropoff
```

